  "prompt": "An autonomous rover explores a volcanic terrain. It collects temperature and seismic data every 200 meters and must not approach closer than 5 meters to lava zones. If terrain slope exceeds 30\u00b0, it activates stabilizers before proceeding. If a data packet fails transmission three times, it must log the failure and continue. Eventually, all checkpoints must be reached and at least 90% of data successfully transmitted.",
